msgid "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:4.5"
msgid "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:4.6"
msgid "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:4.7"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:4.8"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
#. VAR: uppannaṃ lābhaṃ anabhibhuyya → anabhibhuyya anabhibhuyya (mr)
#. VAR: lābhaṃ abhibhuyya → abhibhuyya abhibhuyya (mr)
msgctxt "an8.7:5.1"
msgid "Yaṃ hissa, bhikkhave, uppannaṃ lābhaṃ anabhibhuyya viharato uppajjeyyuṃ āsavā vighātapariḷāhā, uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya viharato evaṃsa te āsavā vighātapariḷāhā na honti. "
msgstr "The distressing and feverish defilements that might arise in someone who lives without overcoming these eight things do not arise when they have overcome them. "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.2"
msgid "Yaṃ hissa, bhikkhave, uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.3"
msgid "uppannaṃ yasaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.4"
msgid "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.5"
msgid "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.6"
msgid "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.7"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.8"
msgid "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ anabhibhuyya viharato uppajjeyyuṃ āsavā vighātapariḷāhā, uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya viharato evaṃsa te āsavā vighātapariḷāhā na honti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.9"
msgid "Idaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu atthavasaṃ paṭicca uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya, "
msgstr "This is the advantage that a mendicant gains by overcoming these eight things. "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.10"
msgid "uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.11"
msgid "uppannaṃ yasaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an8.7:5.12"
